7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Character.ai and Cohere share a solid foundation of core features including Multilingual. Where Character.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Voice Input and Memory, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Cohere uniquely offers Web Search and File Upload and Api Access and Citations, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Character.ai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Cohere scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Character.ai and Cohere offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Character.ai's free tier and Cohere's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
